<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div id="first-card">
        <img src="https://www.inspiredtaste.net/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Pancake-Recipe-1.jpg" alt="Fluffy Pancakes On a Plate">
        <h1>Fluffy Pancakes Recipe</h1>
        <p>These soft and fluffy pancakes are perfect for a quick and delicious breakfast. They are easy to make and require simple ingredients you likely already have at home.</p>
    </div>
    <div id="second-card">
        <h2>Preparation Time</h2>
        <hr>
        <ul>
            <li><span>Prep Time</span> 5 Minutes</li>
            <li><span>Cook Time</span> 10 Minutes</li>
            <li><span>Total Time</span> 15 Minutes</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div id="third-card">
        <h2>Ingredients</h2>
        <hr>
        <ul>
            <li>1 Cup all-purpose floud</li>
            <li>Tablespoon sugar</li>
            <li>1 Cup milk</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div id="fourth-card">
        <h2>Instructions</h2>
        <hr>
        <ol>
            <li>In a bowl, mix flour and sugar, then add milk and stir until smooth.</li>
            <li>Heat a pan over medium heat and pour small portions of batter.</li>
            <li>Cook until bubbles form, flip, and cook the other side until golden.</li>
        </ol>
    </div>
    <div id="fifth-card">
        <h2>Nutrition</h2>
        <hr>
        <p><span>Calories:</span> 220 kcal</p>
        <hr>
        <p><span>Carbs:</span> 30g</p>
        <hr>
        <p><span>Proteins:</span> 6g</p>
        <hr>
        <p><span>Fat:</span> 7g</p>
    </div>    
</body>
</html>
